<H3> <TI>   Clashes Between UNITA, Government Forces Continues </TI></H3>
<H4>   FAA Shelled in Lunda Sul </H4>
<F P=102> MB2102193794 Luanda Radio Nacional Network in Portuguese 
1900 GMT 21 Feb 94 </F>

