<H3> <TI>   Military Spokesman Denies Incursion Into Cameroon </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AB2202170794 Lagos Radio Nigeria Network in English 1500 GMT 
22 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> AB2202170794 </F>
<F P=104>  Lagos Radio Nigeria Network </F>


