Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Reliable sources have told the Voice of Resistance 
of the Black Cockerel that the involvement of a number of 
Namibia Government circles in military and logistical assistance 
to the People's Armed Forces for the Liberation of Angola was 
yesterday discussed at a meeting Lopo do Nascimento [secretary 
