<H3> <TI>   Curfew Imposed in Dead Party Leader's Home Area </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  EA2402194594 Kigali Radiodiffusion Nationale de la 
Republique Rwandaise in Kinyarwanda 1700 GMT 24 Feb 94 </F>

