<H3> <TI>   President Condemns Massacre of Palestinians </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  EA2602201794 Djibouti Radio Djibouti in Somali 1900 GMT 26 
Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> EA2602201794 </F>
<F P=104>  Djibouti Radio Djibouti </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Somali </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] The Republic of Djibouti today condemned in the 
strongest possible terms the brutal massacre of 52 Palestinians 
at a mosque in Hebron, in the West Bank. [passage omitted] 
  Expressing the Djibouti people's anger and strong feelings, 
al- Haji Hassan Gouled Aption, the president of the Republic of 
Djibouti, called for the punishment of the culprits who 
committed the massacre and to bring to an end [word indistinct] 
hostilities flaring up in the Arab regions. 

</TEXT>

