Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The minister of external affairs, Alhaji Babagana 
Kingibe, will brief the nation early next week on the Nigeria- 
Cameroon border issue. The minister of information and culture, 
Professor Jerry Gana, who made this known on Radio Link, said 
