<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "TIYU DA SHICHANG Weekly Published"] </F>
  [Text] The People's Sports Publishing House made two 
valuable gifts to its readers on its 40th founding 
anniversary--the TIYU DA SHICHANG [THE LARGE SPORTS MARKET] and 
a bookshop "Five Rings Book City." 
  The newly published TIYU DA SHICHANG weekly integrates 
sports, consumption, market, and economy into one entity, 
