<H3> <TI>   Anhui's Industrial, Commercial Tax Increases in 1993 </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW3101094494 Hefei ANHUI RIBAO in Chinese 20 Jan 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> OW3101094494 </F>
<F P=104>  Hefei ANHUI RIBAO </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] Total receipts of Anhui Province's industrial 
and commercial taxes topped 7 billion yuan last year. During 
the year the province collected 7.41 billion yuan in industrial 
and commerical tax, registering an increase of 33.6 percent. 
The amount was 990 million yuan higher than the annual quotas, 
and exceeded by 670 million yuan the additional target set for 
our province by the state above and beyond the annual quotas. 
Of which, industrial and commercial taxes collected at local 
levels rose by 1.8 billion yuan, or 34.6 percent, exceeding by 
810 million yuan the revenue target set by the provincial 
government. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

